{
  "texts": [
    "In the future, dynamic and automatic updates of pre-training corpora, as well as self-learning capabilities of LLMs regarding new knowledge, will be crucial research directions.",
    "Quality Assessment.",
    "Longpre et al (2023c) conducts evaluations on The Pile (Gao et al, 2020) and C4 (Raffel et al, 2020), exploring potential features of the data using different data integration methods.",
    "Lee et al (2023a) designs the Task2Vec metric to measure the diversity of data.",
    "However, a systematic methodology for quality assessment has not yet been established."
  ]
}